        "Katana",
        "look",
        "development",
        "RenderMan"
      ]
    },
    {
      "item_id": "5761800d77:1",
      "translation": "RenderMan for Katana (RfK) 为 Katana 用户提供对 RenderMan 强大渲染系统的无缝访问；用户可以利用该 plugin（插件）的灵活性，创建最佳的自定义管线。",
      "words": [
